title: How to Feel Better About Your Life Immediately, with Andy Frisella - MFCEO235

description: How can you keep yourself from feeling like sh*t? There's one thing you can do - or not do - with your mouth that will not only help you preserve your energy and increase your self-respect, but will improve the overall quality & outlook of your life.
